high_descs: Turn left and go to the couch
Grab the phone off of the couch
Turn around and go to the bed
Put the phone on the bed to the right of the pillow
Turn around and go to the black drawer
Grab the phone that is on top of the drawer
Turn around and head to the bed
Put the phone on the bed to the right of the laptop
anns.task_desc: Putting two phones on the bed

high_descs: Walk forward and left to the gray chair.
Pick up the cell phone next to the laptop.
Turn around and walk to the bed.
Put the cell phone on the right side of the first cushion on the left.
Turn around and walk to the long dresser on the left side of the room.
Pick up the cell phone on the dresser.
Turn around and go back to the bed.
Put the cell phone on the left side of the first cushion on the left.
anns.task_desc: Put two cell phones on a bed.

high_descs: Begin walking towards the small blue trash can, then hang a left and walk over to the chair.
Pick the phone up off the seat of the chair.
Turn around, walk over to the end of the bed.
Place the phone on the bed just to the right of the closest pillow to you.
Turn around and walk up to the dresser against the wall.
Pick the blue phone on the dresser up.
Turn around and walk back over to the end of the bed.
Place the phone you are holding to the left of the closest pillow to you.
anns.task_desc: Place a phone on either side of the pillow on the end of the bed.

high_descs: Walk to the sofa chair ahead of you.
Pick up the cell phone from the sofa chair.
Turn around and approach the bed.
Place the cell phone on the bed.
Turn around and walk to the black dresser.
Pick up the cell phone from the dresser.
Turn around and approach the bed.
Place the cell phone on the bed.
anns.task_desc: Place two cell phones on the bed.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the chair with the computer.
Pick up the phone from the chair.
Turn around and walk over to the bed.
Put the phone under the right side of the pillow near the computer.
Turn around and walk over to the black dresser.
Pick up the phone from the black dresser.
Walk back over to the bed.
Put the phone under the left side of the pillow near the computer.
anns.task_desc: Place two phones under the pillow near the computer on the bed.

high_descs: Walk to the trash can and turn left to face the blue chair.
Pick up the cell phone to the right of the lap top.
Turn around and face the foot of the bed.
Put the cell phone down to the right if the cushion that's to the right of the laptop.
Turn around and face the right side of the black dresser.
Pick up the cell phone in front of the yellow pencil.
Turn around and face the foot of the bed again.
Put the phone down to the right of the laptop.
anns.task_desc: To move two cell phones to the foot of the bed.
